HEADWORD: Liederkranz
<hw>Lie"der*kranz</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G. See <ets>Lied</ets>,
and <ets>Grants</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>Lit., wreath of
songs; -- used as the title of a group of songs, and esp. as the common
name for German vocal clubs of men.</def>⟦br⟧
